response.original_title: Bec Hill: Bec in an Hour
response.overview: With an unfeasibly large bag of (mostly reliable) props, and a energetic style that blends kooky irreverence with insightful observation, Aussie Bec Hill brings you a 60-minute greatest-hits set brimming with all her best stuff. Inventive, a little shambolic, and very funny. The joy is well and truly Bec in town.
response.title: Bec Hill: Bec in an Hour
